Resource Profile: FinnishSchedulingAppointment

Official URL: http://hl7.fi/fhir/StructureDefinition/FinnishSchedulingAppointment Version: 0.2.0
Draft as of 2024-08-12 Computable Name: FinnishSchedulingAppointment

Profile for appointment (ajanvaraus) in Finnish Scheduling environment. The contents is based on the scheduling appointment spefication.

Usage:

  • This Resource Profile is not used by any profiles in this Implementation Guide
